{"tid":2361878,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"比特幣站穩4萬美元，惟分析潑冷水估跌50%","createTime":"2021-01-11T05:10:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T12:42:00.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a34f298f5c14dd8ff46045b745343c58d400f9d8","tid":2361878,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T05:10:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DJA.Oer8BFNQblZmWPO6Rg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYxNS4zODQ2MTUzODQ2MTU0/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/17JY9tIcFqCwcTNoYehy9w--~B/aD01MDA7dz03ODA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/608e6305d62f41e5f6dafcaced479369\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FDJA.Oer8BFNQblZmWPO6Rg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYxNS4zODQ2MTUzODQ2MTU0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F17JY9tIcFqCwcTNoYehy9w--~B%2FaD01MDA7dz03ODA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F608e6305d62f41e5f6dafcaced479369&h=9c9862f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7QXckNDuUEQQ0Md4EdtPbyE%3D&h=47e05eb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】據交易平台CryptoCompare數據顯示，比特幣目前升幅約1.4%，報40,769美元。<br />\n<br />\n比特幣近期頻頻破頂，目前企穩4萬美元的高水平，令市場人士擔心高處不勝寒。策略諮詢公司Fundstrat聯合創辦人Tom Lee直言比特幣不穩定，更預測接下來其價格將會腰斬。<br />\n<br />\n外媒報道，Tom Lee認為，比特幣是種極其不穩定的資產。他預測美股會在今年1月底或4月達到高峰，然後標普500指數會在4,000點附近開始大幅下跌，如果標指跌10%，比特幣將出現重挫，跌幅可能介乎40至50%。但他補充，綜觀比特幣過去走勢，這是個相當平常的過程，隨之而來會現現大反撲，今年比特幣漲幅料仍超過3倍。<br />\n<br />\n他舉例說，如果看起來像2017年，認為比特幣至少會上漲300%，不認為比特幣走勢會像直尺一樣直線上升，而是會像鋸齒狀般，但到了今年年底，比特幣價格會更高。<br />\n<br />\n由於比特幣走勢大上大落，即使備受追捧，卻有不少人視之為「金融騙局」。華爾街「大淡友」Rosenberg Research總裁羅森堡直指比特幣泡沫嚴重，形容在如此短的時間內，其「拋物線」走勢極度不正常。虛擬貨幣平台Celsius Network首席執行官Alex Mashinsky亦「潑冷水」，稱比特幣不排除首季會低見1.6萬美元。"},{"pid":"83568660bc14b1457e65e03d575f41546b10ecf2","tid":2361878,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:42:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}